Configuration stuff to build an IPS (Solaris 11) style package and
publish to a local IPS repository (or via the OmniOS "extra" repository)

OmniOSCE info on their build system:
https://www.pbdigital.org/omniosce/packaging/2020/03/30/extra-builds-omniosce.html

Oracle info on how to create IPS packages:
https://www.oracle.com/technical-resources/articles/it-infrastructure/admin-o11-097-create-pkg-ips.html



